{"tid":1942701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"20歲男子承認藏汽油彈 還押等候判刑","createTime":"2020-03-25T08:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T03:32:24.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b82869fd5b0faf6ee93a64cabd9b2ee32fd377","tid":1942701,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:32:15.000Z","msg":"20歲男子承認藏汽油彈 還押等候判刑<br />\n<br />\n1名20歲男子涉嫌去年在旺角藏有汽油彈，在西九龍裁判法院，承認1項管有攻擊性武器，押後至下月8日判刑，期間需要還押。<br />\n<br />\n案發在去年9月7日，一批示威者包圍旺角警署，警員在旺角洗衣街行人天橋截查拘捕被告，帶到警車搜查，在背囊發現有1支汽油彈、打火機、頭盔和保護衣。被告在警誡下承認，有人將玻璃樽交給他。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1276316&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1276316%26csid%3D261_341&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=e2c6b4cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1276316&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"e355d97f76db352f0fb332ba2d86e73485e192fb","tid":1942701,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:33:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9151c18b089c7473bd725c5f4b80909f0cf57fa6","tid":1942701,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1945c6ee73f8661255024dddb30068fdd1e727cc","tid":1942701,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:33:56.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"87d